title: Episode 314: SMD from the Back! (Feat. Chinese Kitty)
itunes:title: Episode 314: SMD from the Back! (Feat. Chinese Kitty)
description:
Rapper, Chinese Kitty joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her new album "SMD." Kitty and the crew share ideas regarding what defines 'good dick,' being lied on by men, and much more. Chinese Kitty shares a wild story in which she was betrayed by an ex, as well as clarifying the nonsense she had to deal with while flying coach on a recent flight. Enjoy!
